import streamlit as st


st.write("Mapbox has two search-related APIs: the Mapbox Geocoding API and the Mapbox Search API. The Mapbox Geocoding API allows you to do forward and reverse geocoding operations. Forward Geocoding takes text in the form of an address or place and converts it to geographic coordinates (latitude/longitude). Reverse geocoding takes geographic coordinates (latitude/longitude) and converts it into an address or place in text form.")